# MASS L3 TDL — 第三方库 vendor（git submodule）
# 详见: docs/Implementation/third-party-library-policy.md §2.1 + §5.1
# 强约束（F-CRIT-A-006 修复）：每个 submodule 必须锁定到具体 tag/branch（非浮动 main/master）
# 初始化命令: git submodule update --init --recursive

[submodule "tools/third-party/eigen-5.0.0"]
	path = tools/third-party/eigen-5.0.0
	url = https://gitlab.com/libeigen/eigen.git
	branch = 5.0.0

[submodule "tools/third-party/nlohmann-json-3.12.0"]
	path = tools/third-party/nlohmann-json-3.12.0
	url = https://github.com/nlohmann/json.git
	branch = v3.12.0

